{"tid":2436916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐「自由鳳梨」外媒轟京貿易威脅","createTime":"2021-03-07T13:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:43:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe3ef68b9547e68a220976194d7b01b5876b6f4","tid":2436916,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/RIG5RTYSEFBXNB4NM2HB3GVVOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2FRIG5RTYSEFBXNB4NM2HB3GVVOY%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bBT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=24f2f7c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2FRIG5RTYSEFBXNB4NM2HB3GVVOY%2F&h=4287b32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/RIG5RTYSEFBXNB4NM2HB3GVVOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n撐「自由鳳梨」外媒轟京貿易威脅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dRRUSu_Yh-QNZA7e7ZE-3BP9Eqs=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GAG5XOL52VFBLCUQWW2O5Y6BVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdRRUSu_Yh-QNZA7e7ZE-3BP9Eqs%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGAG5XOL52VFBLCUQWW2O5Y6BVY.jpg&h=5b6c2168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■高雄有商家舉辦促銷活動，客人買一杯飲料就有「西施」親自贈送鳳梨一顆。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n大陸禁止台灣鳳梨進口，西方媒體亦廣泛關注，意大利主流報章《共和報》報道事件中指，北京經常以貿易作為武器，向其他地方的政府施壓，至於加拿大報章《國家郵報》（National Post）也就 「鳳梨之戰」在當地時間3日作出橫跨三個版面的報道。<br />\n<br />\n《共和報》指，台灣與大陸關係惡化，鳳梨成為最新的受害者。報道提及去年中國對澳洲紅酒徵收反傾銷稅，引來多國聲援，當時台灣總統蔡英文也力撐澳洲紅酒，而美國和加拿大已為鳳梨發聲，並稱北京經常以貿易制裁作為武器，採取可能對其他地方造成重大經濟損失的行動，藉此向對方施加壓力。<br />\n<br />\n而意大利國營電視台Rai News則報道，台灣民眾團結響應政府呼籲挽救自產鳳梨，短短四天內購買比進口中國還要多的鳳梨數量，又指日本似乎決定在這場戰局中，採取可能會惹怒北京的立場，台灣鳳梨外銷日本已經創下超過5,000噸的新高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加《國家郵報》多版報道<br />\n<br />\n加拿大《國家郵報》則以橫跨三個版面來報道事件，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VEe9P5YTenGZDJXjwEwu5h3_N1s=/787x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YOFPYAZT4NCNBMAR6A7VLUFO7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVEe9P5YTenGZDJXjwEwu5h3_N1s%3D%2F787x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYOFPYAZT4NCNBMAR6A7VLUFO7Q.jpg&h=04873c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣鳳梨（左）和菲律賓菠蘿（右）的外皮和葉子有明顯差別。"},{"pid":"227ffa2b057a5ede9446b967ed3ed0e31670d072","tid":2436916,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1e331854d41bccbb94eefa84a377d68bf792fcd","tid":2436916,"uid":76133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86ee0011b7465216315fcccdcc43fb802c528b8","tid":2436916,"uid":276989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"訂咗2箱20隻聽日到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbadaf0411472cd6bb70d2aaefea9f1103df1aeb","tid":2436916,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDjsGs3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDjsGs3.gif&h=1ece8564&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"210b97fb74a5209d5ddd717cfc158c2f3a9953cc","tid":2436916,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86ee0011b7465216315fcccdcc43fb802c528b8","tid":2436916,"uid":276989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"訂咗2箱20隻聽日到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"食唔食得晒呀<br />\n搵人夾份訂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow